{"tid":914390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[雞蟲末日？]強國約125萬人染愛滋病　異性扑野感染佔七成","createTime":"2018-11-24T08:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T09:42:51.000Z","uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0d52ac0366b71381479652715d83618eac24f665","tid":914390,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"國家衛生健康委員會（國家衛健委）周五（23日）公布，截至今年底，估計全中國愛滋病感染者約有125萬，感染率為萬分之九，與其他國家相比屬「低流行水平」，新增感染病例每年則估計約有8萬宗。目前性接觸是國內愛滋病主要傳播途徑，其中近七成感染者是經異性性接觸染病，男男性接觸傳播則佔約兩成半。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國家衛健委表示，截至今年9月底，全國已報告的愛滋病存活感染者有85萬人，26.2萬人死亡，估計每年新增8萬宗感染病例。據中國疾控中心、聯合國愛滋病規劃署及世界衛生組織聯合評估，至今年底，國內存活愛滋病感染者將達125萬人。<br />\n<br />\n目前性接觸是國內愛滋病主要傳播途徑，2017年已報告的感染者中，69.6%經異性性接觸染病；經男男性接觸受感染者，則佔總染病人口25.5%。另外，2017年愛滋病母嬰傳播率為4.9%，是歷來最低水平，比2012年低2.2個百分點；經注射吸毒感染者，則比2012年減少44.5%；經輸血及使用血液製品傳播病例「接近零報告」。<br />\n<br />\n根據去年全年數檢，愛滋病抗病毒治療覆蓋率為80.4%，治療「成功率」超過90%。國家衛健委疾病預防控制局副局長王斌表示，往後將提高預防愛滋病宣傳教育的針對性；由於國內愛滋病疫情分佈不平均，當局將加強重點地區及「易感染愛滋病危險行為人群」的「警示性」教育，及推廣使用安全套預防愛滋病和性病等；亦會推廣檢測、諮詢、診斷和治療「一站式」服務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/24/XgEvQx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F24%2FXgEvQx.png&h=d8fd3514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168e49113b8354a24c1d404abb57f1428319c62e","tid":914390,"uid":26752,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:33:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又</span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"17f18b1ee17b63de5297874b4a23d51e67387584","tid":914390,"uid":207254,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:48:39.000Z","msg":"認真一問 呢啲統計計唔計埋香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63c52b7e834e5c5280fd9252706f3a31c63a95e","tid":914390,"uid":202354,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:01:47.000Z","msg":"很多基佬都有愛滋病<br />\n很多連登仔是基佬<br />\n很多連登仔有愛滋病<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16cef3341d7f82b05cf4bacf91f73afcfe730c86","tid":914390,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:05:31.000Z","msg":"條數好假。如果係就唔會有咁多愛滋村啦"},{"pid":"6d6c2ab89c149c009d3ac3daf2f18ff52a6c17af","tid":914390,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:09:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">child登cc台弱智：<br />\n冇可能㗎！<br />\n愛g9全部都係gay佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"c36ccc9be056235f0be5cda9fb8296ddded92987","tid":914390,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:10:41.000Z","msg":"發夢夢到佢地好識保護自己<br />\n會用兩個安全套， 雙重保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d24a38b040c40e628bb161900448f0249b5e2d9","tid":914390,"uid":218082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:13:45.000Z","msg":"學CC台反同撚:散播愛滋大部份都係異性戀,啲雞蟲同蟲都好撚嘔心好核突要全部絕種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢班友柒夠未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a21528d2caa93555eb3d15d522f09dbc03dd551","tid":914390,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"同支那人造愛者愛滋死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643fbbb525f97e5c8eb4c3481191f8a0c304dab